data.text: Hammerheads are a species of sharks native to Port Clovis. The second largest predatory shark in Port Clovis, these strange-looking sharks reside in Crawfish Bay, Sapphire Bay, Prosperity Sands, Caviar Keys, and The Gulf. They're also included in the Plover Island Complex, only to be a normal, but a larger version of the hammerhead shark which is a reused Hunted Hammerhead.
